data.description: Upgraded, modern, and move in ready! Beautiful wood floors that seamlessly flow throughout the entire downstairs. The kitchen is equipped with double ovens, a gas stove, stunning cabinetry, adorned with elegant granite countertops, and a breakfast bar. Incredible and unique floor plan where the main level features 3 bedrooms, accompanied by two full bathrooms, as well a formal room. Spacious family room, where a floor-to-ceiling gas fireplace serves as a striking focal point. Natural light and sunshine pours in through the wall of windows in the primary bedroom. Upstairs, an expansive area awaits, offering versatility as a fourth bedroom, game room, or media room and is accompanied by a full bathroom. Close walk to the community pool and park. Additionally, this home is part of the highly sought-after Keller Independent School District, ensuring an exceptional education for your family.
